SkyCart Help Center

Get answers to your questions and learn how to use SkyCart

Frequently Asked Questions

How do I track my order?

You can track your order by going to "Your Orders" in your account and clicking on the tracking number provided.

What is your return policy?

We offer a 30-day return policy for most items. Items must be in original condition and packaging.

How do I cancel an order?

You can cancel an order within 1 hour of placing it by going to "Your Orders" and clicking "Cancel Order".

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, PayPal, and digital wallets like Apple Pay and Google Pay.

How do I change my shipping address?

You can update your shipping address in your account settings under "Addresses" or during checkout.
